                            <comment id="17849745" author="soarez" created="Mon, 27 May 2024 14:16:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=robinhan&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;robinhan&quot;&gt;robinhan&lt;/a&gt;. Thanks for filling this.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Can you say a bit more about step &quot;4. Upgrade Broker B to 3.7.0;&quot;? Are you setting inter.broker.protocol.version? Or is this the step where the broker binary/jar changes?&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Kafka source before 3.7 is unable to set a value for directory assignments. Since the missing (default) value assumes MIGRATING, I&apos;m not sure how in step 4 we run into UNASSIGNED.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
